@* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   Global Blazor imports for SmartERP.Wpf
   Namespaces reflect the 'namespace' declarations in each .cs/.razor file.
   RootNamespace in the .csproj is "SmartERP", so all paths begin with SmartERP.
   DO NOT change these to SmartERP.Wpf.* — those namespaces do not exist.
   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── *@

